title: Disaster Dates
description:
In this episode Jessi and Stew recall their dating disasters and tell funny stories about past dates that they're still recovering from. Alsooo, we discovered Stew's mic was broken which is why his voice was a lot softer in the first three episodes. But no worries, we got him a new one so now he's loud and proud again!
